Name: Cannon Jump

FEATURES Atmospheric graphics and soundtrack High jumps Long jumps Precise jumps Inaccurate jumps Jumping up Falls - - - This game was inspired by Jump King and Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy. - - - 'In shooter games, rocket jumping is the technique of using the knockback of an explosive weapon, most often a rocket launcher, to launch the shooter into the air.
